headline: Otter is now a DoorDash Preferred Integration Partner
summary: Today at the National Restaurant Association Show in Chicago, DoorDash announced the launch of its Preferred Integrations Partner Program and named Otter as one of the program's inaugural partners. This certification highlights Otter's best-in-class DoorDash integration, offering restaurants rich features and secure and stable performance.
